{
  "text": "Recent research exploring how students interact with ChatGPT has shown that many university students are already using AI, specifically using it to proofread their assignments (Črček & Patekar, 2023; Singh et al., 2023), and it was found to be comparable to humans (Heintz et al., 2022).",
